## Rules / Configuration

No formal rules file or MCP server configuration was used. Claude was accessed through
the standard claude.ai web interface. Prompts were conversational and iterative.

---

## What AI Did NOT Do

- AI did not write the core application logic from scratch
- AI did not design the database schema
- AI did not build the HTML core structure
- AI did not generate the resume preview or print layout logic
- The student wrote, reviewed, and understood all code in this project

---

## Statement of Understanding

All code in this project — including any sections assisted by AI — has been reviewed
and is understood by the student. Any AI-generated or AI-assisted code that differs
from what was covered in class has been researched and can be explained verbally.
